Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:25.75,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,請問請問　現在是甚麼顏色呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:28.29,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容的白色　淚水的藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:31.06,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,將它們重疊在一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:36.55,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天氣晴朗　外出郊遊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:39.02,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,進行冰牛奶彈珠汽水特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:41.83,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,代表精神的顏色正充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:45.66,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,喂－！　喜歡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:51.81,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,請來進行大家的肖像畫素描比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:59.02,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,好－吧！　之後可別「砰」的一下就生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:04.15,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,被人按下按鈕時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:06.27,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:12.59,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得只要開心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:17.03,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽吧　看誰蘋果吃得快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:23.31,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣　急躁起來好嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:27.98,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,水果便是模特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:36.04,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,來　開始素描吧　這是作業哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山吹文化節當日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.82,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（山吹文化節！）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.34,0:00:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  好美的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是做到很晚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她再睡會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先把畫拿展覽室去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「11月3日  由乃殿下」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然睡過頭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畫不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小宮～～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  之前放這裡的畫  哪兒去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我搬到展覽室去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客人來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了今天由乃可是很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…其實那畫還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也得抓緊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是舞臺劇的準備時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一趟展覽室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已經沒有這時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：C•莫奈，1840-1926，法國印象派畫家）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：W•莎士比亞，這個不用解釋了吧…）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:31.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（難以抉擇）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.31,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（體育館）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好個貪婪下賤的丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.81,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（「灰姑娘」）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能有為你準備的禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是  你在家裡老實待著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去把浴室也打掃一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  手不停地顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學  絕妙的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畫我先搬過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那畫正在展出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是沒有完成的狀態…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本想一直畫到早上的話能像點樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然睡著了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然睡著了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.06,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（居然睡著了……）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一幕的背景光一直是黃色？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我這種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆一直因為被紡錘扎了手而沉睡下去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:21.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（語出自《睡美人》，這個似乎沒必要注釋了…）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學  那就不是灰姑娘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣  灰姑娘就這樣一直幸福地生活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以上是美術科一年A班演出的「灰姑娘」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  演得不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學  幫我們大忙了  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同學們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師  不要連您也哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在後夜祭的演出被取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:51.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：“後夜祭”，學園祭最後一天的晚上舉行， 一般就是圍著火堆跳跳舞啦甚麼的…）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易急中生智想出來的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校長卻說「絕對不行」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象還能聽見掌聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  有好多觀眾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我去看展覽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮和由乃都有很活躍的表現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐你們的舞臺劇已經結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因為我們是上午第一出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:24.29,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  沙英學姐不在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,演出怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過背對著我會遭殃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,評價非常不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們之後還有甚麼演出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有的話出去逛逛那些攤位怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃不  我倒沒說要請客…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃過飯後  下午就悠閒地看看展覽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,展覽  展覽  展覽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說我很想一起去吃飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我…我還是先去看展覽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在還不餓…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（人聲嘈雜）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.79,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（希望能折斷它  美術科教員  吉野屋）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:23.79,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（美術科個人作品展覽室）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又想快點看…又不想看…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  但是果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是我睏了記不大清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是畫完之後才睡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:43.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（文化節的準備  1-A  美術科  由乃）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情壓根就不會去當真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,文化節的準備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很不錯的畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？但…但是畫的下部…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:06:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,空著的地方是代表畫這畫的由乃同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,tururu～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是表示準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太…太高估我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管如何對觀眾解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說這畫始終是沒有完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒能把我想畫的全都畫上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,展覽結束之後  把它畫完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這份懊悔的心情我要好好保存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信這經歷一定會讓我成長的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是小學生嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那不是我們學校的運動衫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我喜歡這畫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是由乃的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畫下正在準備的大家  這想法很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這視角非常的溫柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  這個空白的地方是重點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡空著才是「正在畫」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:58.73,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部畫完了就不是「準備」了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:00.53,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮你的作品在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是真人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃困了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不  昨晚睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我覺得還是會疲勞的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說現在睡著了可能就起不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天開始又是同平時一樣要上課了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得…怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不變回平常的樣子也不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是明天也和今天一樣就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼快就得回到現實中來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會發傳真來的就只有編輯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是來催稿子的吧  大概
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:02.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:03.55,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,回音…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:04.16,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:04.84,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:05.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,我要過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不高興了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？是甚麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  轉啊轉啊轉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  來啊來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？來做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊看啊  大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,汝亦有過…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非也  此乃惡代官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:33.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：代官，某地方官一般的角色）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi  同學們  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.41,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（山吹）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山吹文化節過得很愉快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不希望結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,L•o•v•e
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Lovely  吉野屋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的演出現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋登場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對淘氣的壞孩子 就要用打針來懲罰～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:02.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（這個nurse的cosplay…臺詞來源大概是逮捕令裡\N辻本夏実那句極其經典的“逮捕しちゃうぞ”）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  如果再能有一天的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在想這個也沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃你很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  還是沒來得及…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你確實是努力過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是都看在眼裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常專注呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發覺我們在屋子裡了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我們偷偷跑去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是很在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在由乃不知道的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們組成了守護由乃協會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  讓你們操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  沒甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能更早開始的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做甚麼這個問題非常難辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  就是在這上面花了不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是「做甚麼都好」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有限制倒更加難辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心情我理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能找到可以商量的人我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…要是能想出更好的建議就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是在由乃來找我商量的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定了自己要做甚麼去參展
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？那時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看著由乃那萬般苦惱而無以言表的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想到應該畫下來保存起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那好難為情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我也去找過吉野屋老師的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她和你商量了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不是那狀況…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校長對她發脾氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是關於吉野屋老師的表演有些爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那是自然不成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這衣服也以太過sexy的理由被否決了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同學們能看到實在是太走運了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來為甚麼會做那幅畫呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起了岸學姐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,契機無處不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的東西也一直在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我發現了這個「重要的東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不讓我穿這衣服的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就跳肚皮舞好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：belly dance，西亞北非地區比較風行，\N顧名思義，就是露出肚皮跳舞…）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腦子裡一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,臺詞怎麼也想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過大伙也隨機應變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順利地演下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能背對著他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要正對著就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就能說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挺遠的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  還有一段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我想或許能消除疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還真遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能大伙兒一起去我挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我之前一直無所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人的話就覺得突然變安靜了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀  是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  可以看見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  煙囪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海水浴？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：她說的是“塩の湯”，指加熱海水用來洗澡的…）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是淡水浴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：大概為某名溫泉名或名浴室名…）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做成從前那種浴池的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蠻有情趣  挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃殿下？誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.38,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：日文和上文的“淡水浴”順序正好是顛倒的…）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼  為甚麼由乃是VIP？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨  四百日圓一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一文不少  四百日圓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:13:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後這是最後一百
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒洗就喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:15.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（臉上火辣辣的…）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀呵  溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像畫裡的浴池一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  好大的澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的凳子可以隨便用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要先洗身子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小宮  危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  輪到由乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能一直浸到肩膀真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直挺挺地坐下去是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:08.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（新橋牙科醫院  日和田醫院  …新竹）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,浴池的牆真畫的是富士山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說各個澡堂都不大一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這還是經久不衰的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話就要畫壯美的雪山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就能清楚感覺到溫暖的溫泉的那份難得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得雷諾阿的畫不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.48,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：Renoir(1841-1919)，法國印象派畫家，\N以肖像畫特別是女性畫見長，亦是女性形象崇拜者）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒覺得根本不合適…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女人就是要豐滿才有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像很開心呢  小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能到達這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就稱讚你一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（boss或裝boss者專用臺詞…）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想說說看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  你是喜歡從頭開始洗的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  那閉眼睛的樣子像小學生一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為香波會弄到眼睛裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山吹文化節真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底那個班級是最受歡迎的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是三年級的鬼屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  德古伯爵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼討厭大蒜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為很難聞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他鼻子非常好使的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和狗一樣靈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  這樣啊  他還會變身成狼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？德拉庫拉變的是蝙蝠吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該也會變狼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,德拉庫拉是蝙蝠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  確實也會變狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是蝙蝠啦  沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也無所謂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃一直纏著毛巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難為情？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不大習慣和別人一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我常和妹妹一起所以或許習慣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好想有個和沙英學姐一樣的哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得有些漫長又覺得有些短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有很難受的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過努力過了還是好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  完全燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是有點燃燒不充分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在說那畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你已經決定要畫完它了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  完成了你們願意來看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  校長做了些甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？我好象隱約看到了他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校長也沒有展示甚麼自己的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本還有點期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許現在開始做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄斷了的吉野屋老師的塑像甚麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  這話太惡毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能說不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吹電風扇去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,展覽上看到熏衣草的畫了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也挺喜歡那個的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到那畫的時候就覺得沙英學姐可能會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說到讓人眼前一亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是那個  三年級學生做的那高達四米的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,半魚人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有氣勢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過為甚麼是半魚人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像說是想做個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是平衡性很難掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就弄成了半魚人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣行嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,舞臺劇的話出演了自己班上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說看過的話就只有由乃你們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涼了的身子又慢慢地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說小宮  再演一次馬來看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想賤賣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對小宮演的馬感到吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛聽到的時候也是嚇一大跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,南瓜做的馬車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:12.69,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}灰姑娘\N南瓜馬車\N魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:12.69,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}馬\N宮子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乘上這個去參加舞會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  謝謝您  老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是女孩子為甚麼演馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和南瓜一樣用大道具表現不就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爆相似
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.81,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（新橋牙科醫院  日和田醫院  …新竹  …花田）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贏得滿場喝彩呢  一鳴驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學也很引人注目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以上是美術科一年A班演出的「灰姑娘」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？哎呀好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照明過來幫我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幕布合不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒不想太顯眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  有兩下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  想反擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說由乃  舞臺劇時有一個地方看著不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說你們倆也是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坐你們邊上的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像一直吃個沒停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烏賊燒對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她弄出聲音來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們因為太暗也沒看清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先是烏賊燒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後是炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接著是羊肉串
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最後吃的是豬排飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  豬排飯是我憑嗅覺知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能吃得下這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想吃豬排飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該早上第一個就跑去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,限量三十份的豬排飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛聽說ICHIBIN的蛋糕很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跑去就賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要去一趟ICHIBIN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向他們請教菜譜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:20:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們也嘗嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍…稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都有些不捨得出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地擦乾了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擦乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐一點也不胖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說不胖…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這鏡子好像是芭蕾教室裡用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前面再安個扶手就是了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,練繃腿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直燒著熱水就出去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.13,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：其實日語裡熱水和溫泉是同一個字“湯”）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就變涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有些可惜了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  今天一定能睡得很甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,舒舒服服地睡上一覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之今天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11月3日  完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待續
