Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:43.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（中山動物園）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,便當順帶的小菜要甚麼好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡煎蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡臘腸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  螃蟹和章魚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,節日裡就是要吃壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.17,0:23:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三角的三角的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有時是圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面也是圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  飯團吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:24:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記東西或是遲到可是不行的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「4月28日  圓圓的捲心菜」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在山吹高中等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要來看哦
